{"tid":2179552,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫來講，潮與虎都算係世界第二","createTime":"2020-08-29T07:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T17:29:08.000Z","uid":43785,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0d9e4c8e26eafb88c4e50dab4b57aaebbd3a63","tid":2179552,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"漫畫來講，潮與虎都算係世界第二。<br />\n<br />\n成套漫畫玩雙主角，內容極度完整，伏筆真係教科書級別，鋼練都未係佢果個LV，<br />\n由頭到尾一個BOSS貫穿過去未來同成個故事，一氣呵成。<br />\n要熱血有熱血，要感動有感動。<br />\n親情友情愛情友情人妖情乜都有。<br />\n前面出過唔起眼既人物，後面全部有作用。<br />\n<br />\n最後成個故事忽然大逆轉，由輕鬆變左另一境界。<br />\n結局估你唔到會變到咁。<br />\n<br />\n一套作品玩一人一妖，寫得太撚癲，搞到呢幾十年D王道卡通動漫不停抄佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一作者魔偶有睇，但真係唔及潮與虎果重直接同震撼。<br />\n就連作者都叫你，如果受唔住，就唔好睇落去，真係串撚到呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漫畫來講，潮與虎都算係世界第二。"},{"pid":"ffa91b04d089d275c40bcd61b3df3ed2df389e29","tid":2179552,"uid":133377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"警察故事算係世界第一"},{"pid":"4150553c282df21c0f2cd6a3e54f47461fb32eb7","tid":2179552,"uid":312193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0UKuT1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0UKuT1.gif&h=ea5ee1e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf5b4ae8cb74a50bdf4c6348fe7489341bfe2d79","tid":2179552,"uid":227628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db9d6ea92109d8509cb97821fbd471c3fcfc6a0","tid":2179552,"uid":49201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"Yes sir"},{"pid":"0d6ec3b52e7dfd9a59fccebffcff39608c3dc17c","tid":2179552,"uid":261505,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir !<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=